Summary: Driving home witness A reported seeing a large V-shaped fromation of very bright lights move over his car from East to West.
divs: Sighting DetailsWitness A was driving home about 8:15 pm and observed a low V-shaped formation of lights move East to West over him. The lights were too bright to to see a shape. Witness was only a minute or two from his home and after arriving home the object was gone.
